#  quality ~ alcohol 
m1 <- lm(I(quality) ~ I(alcohol), data=ww)
# m1 rate.sulfur.dioxide
m2 <- update(m1, ~ . + rate.sulfur.dioxide)
# m2 chlorides
m3 <- update(m2, ~ . + chlorides)
# m3 density
m4 <- update(m3, ~ . + density)
mtable(m1,m2,m3,m4)
